
SOURCE 
https://www.forbes.com/sites/omribarzilay/2017/11/14/trueaccord-nabs-22m-series-b-to-bring-machine-learning-to-debt-collections/#112c6d1b7f09
AGENT
TrueAccord
GOAL
The goal is to disrupt the debt collection industry.
DATA
They used their 1.8 million customers as data.
METHOD
They used a machine learning algorithm to analyse customer trends. They then tailored their debt collection methods to each customer based off what was successful with similar customers.
RESULT
The algorithm had a minimum increase of 50% (to 500%) in debt collection rates.
